  "markup": "Dr. Christopher Carraway of LTU, interviews Praveen Arany, DDS, PhD (President of NAALT) Assistant Clinical Investigator, National Institute of Dental \u0026amp; Craniofacial Research, Bethesda, Maryland at the NAALT/WALT joint meeting in Washington, DC, September 2014.\u0026nbsp; Dr. Arany highlights his vision for NAALT going forward, and reviews this years conference agenda and reasons to attend and belong to the national association."
}]]></Value>
